f particular note is the presentation of a form of graph-based\ninduction, allowing the formal encoding of proofs that previously could only be\nrepresented as a mix of string diagrams and explanatory text.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 30 Mar 2014 22:55:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-01"}
