-linear Schottky regime. In the intermediate voltage regime,\nthe cross-ratio changes sign and diverges, which evidences a change of sign in\nthe heat cross-noise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Mar 2014 15:03:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 17 May 2014 13:21:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 20 Jul 2014 09:49:54 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 11 Dec 2014 15:11:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-12"}
